<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.2.6">
<l>paṇaṅka ḷāyira muṭaiyanal laravaṇaip</l>
<l>paḷḷikoṭ paramāveṉ</l>
<l>ṟiṇaṅki vāṉavar maṇimuṭi paṇitara</l>
<l>viruntanal limayattu</l>
<l>maṇaṅkoṇ mātavi neṭuṅkoṭi vicumpuṟa</l>
<l>nimirntavai mukiṟpaṟṟi</l>
<l>piṇaṅku pūmpoḻiṉ ṉuḻaintuvaṇ ṭicaicolum piriticeṉ ṟaṭaineñcē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>In the fair Himalayas where [he] resides</l>
<l rend="indent">as celestials bow their jewel-crowned [heads], saying in unison,</l>
<l>“Supreme who sleeps on the bed that is a fine serpent with a thousand hoods,”</l>
<l>[My] heart, go and take refuge at Piriti where bees hum melodies,</l>
<l rend="indent">creeping in entangled flower groves</l>
<l>Of long fragrant mādhavi creepers stretching to reach heaven,</l>
<l rend="indent">catching at the clouds.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
